genresAdvancedInfo.name: chinderlieder
genresAdvancedInfo.description: This Swiss genre of music is specifically created for children. It incorporates simple melodies, catchy lyrics, and interactive elements to engage young listeners and encourage them to sing along. Chinderlieder often feature playful themes and use a variety of instruments to create a fun and upbeat atmosphere.
